Hi,
I'm trying to get the pointer to the decoded byte array of SKImage, but it always returns null. I also tried with ToRasterImage, but the result is the same.

My code:

SKData data = SKData.Create("test.bmp");
SKImage img = SKImage.FromEncodedData(data);
SKPixmap pix = img.PeekPixels(); <--- NULL
IntPtr ptr = pix.GetPixels();

many thanks
